# PATHFIND::SET_ALLOW_STREAM_PROLOGUE_NODES

## Parameters
* **BOOL** allow

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Set to TRUE to allow prologue road nodes from being
loaded, FALSE to disable
